                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-1176" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN KIRK</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a labourer at St. Katherine's Docks. I saw the prisoner cut four ropes off part of the bales—he left the ropes in the wagon.</p>
